- repository structure?
  steamlink/steamlink-store -> pypi package
  steamlink/steamlink-node	-> arduino library w/ samples

- to make a new release on pypi
	cd ~/git/steamlink
	vi steamlink/const.py   edit *_VERSION
	git commit -a -m "version 0.7.1"
	git push
	git tag 0.7.1 -m "0.7.1"	
	git push --tags origin master

	. ~/sl/bin/activate
	
	python3 setup.py sdist upload -r pypi
	
